              We don't have any specific positions open at the moment, but we're always interested in meeting talented people. Send us your resume and let us know how you could contribute to our mission.
            </p>
            <a 
              href="mailto:careers@getlinkme.app" 
              class="inline-block bg-indigo-600 hover:bg-indigo-700 text-white font-medium py-2 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-200"
            >
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        )}
      </div>
    </Container>
  </section>
  
  <!-- Application Process Section -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <Container>
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">
            Our Hiring Process
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
            We've designed our hiring process to be thorough but efficient, giving both you and us the opportunity to determine if we're the right fit for each other.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="space-y-12">
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">
                01
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                Application Review
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                Our team reviews your application, resume, and any additional materials you've submitted. We look for relevant experience, skills, and alignment with our values.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
