                02
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                Initial Phone Screen
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                A brief call with our recruiting team to discuss your background, interest in LinkMe, and answer any initial questions you might have about the role and company.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
