                03
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                Skills Assessment
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                Depending on the role, we may ask you to complete a brief assignment or technical challenge to demonstrate your skills and problem-solving approach. We respect your time and design these to be completed within 2-3 hours.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
