            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">
                04
              </div>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-2">
                Team Interviews
              </h3>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                You'll meet with potential teammates and cross-functional partners to discuss your experience, skills, and how you'd contribute to LinkMe. We also want you to get to know us and ask questions.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 mr-6">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-indigo-100 dark:bg-indigo-900 flex items-center justify-center text-lg font-bold text-indigo-600 dark:text-indigo-400">
                05
